
Step One: Search "Service Catalog" > "Create New"

Step Two: Under Report Name, fill out a new name.

Step Three: Source Type: Table

Step Four: Table: Task

Step Five: Conditions > Active ------------ is ------------ True
                        Assignment Group -- is ------------ Managers
                        Created ----------- at or before -- This Week

Step Six: Type > Bar (or whichever you prefer)

Step Seven: Configure > Group By > Assignment Group

Step Eight: Style ... (configure as desired)
